  "texts": [
    "Key characteristics of each model are presented in Table 1.For this study, we did not have access to individual patient data that were used in the published models to fit overall survival, progression-free survival and time-to-discontinuation curves.",
    "Therefore, these extrapolated curves were used directly as parameters in the AI-generated models.",
    "To constrain the scope of our case study, we generated only the base case analyses, and sensitivity and scenario analyses were not included.",
    "Overview of the LLM-Based Automation of Model ConstructionAn overview of the LLM-based automation of model construction, including the prompt development process, is shown in Fig. 2.",
    "Prompt Development ProcessLLMs generate text content based on inputs known as 'prompts'."
